 class=\"tableLine\">1/100&nbsp;000–1/999&nbsp;999</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Blod-, lever- och njurskador<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">Mukokutant syndrom</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Sulfonamider, NSAID<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">Antiepileptika</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Flygolyckor</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\" class=\"footNotes\"><div class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_18\">a. <div class=\"tableLine\">HRT = hormonal replacement treatment.</div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>"
