				"number": 7,
				"title": "<a class=\"crossref\" id=\"40704\"></a>Läkemedel som kan orsaka rytmrubbningar",
				"id": "x3_44",
				"text": "<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Rytmrubbningar</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Läkemedel</strong></div></td><td><p><strong><div class=\"tableLine\">Effekt på autonoma </div><div class=\"tableLine\">nervsystemet</div></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><div class=\"tableLine\">Direkt effekt på <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">de- och repolarisation i </div><div class=\"tableLine\">retledningssystem och </div><div class=\"tableLine\">myocyter</div></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Supraventrikulära </div><div class=\"tableLine\">takyarytmier</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Antikolinerga läkemedel</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">+</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Kalciumantagonister och </div><div class=\"tableLine\">beta-2-stimulerare</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Reflektorisk takykardi se-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">kundärt till kärldilatation</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Antiarytmika klass I och III</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">+</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Supraventrikulära </div><div class=\"tableLine\">bradyarytmier inkl </div><div class=\"tableLine\">överledningsrubb-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">ningar</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Betablockerare</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">+</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Verapamil, karbamazepin </div><div class=\"tableLine\">och litium</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">+</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Digitalis</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">+</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Kammararytmier</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Antiarytmika klass I och III</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">+</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Digitalis och tricykliska <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">antidepressiva vid intoxi-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">kation</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">+</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Torsade de pointes</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Sotalol, fluorokinoloner, </div><div class=\"tableLine\">neuroleptika och makrolider</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">+</div></td></tr></tbody></table>"
