				"number": 12,
				"title": "<a class=\"crossref\" id=\"71753\"></a>Några läkemedel (läkemedels&shy;grupper) som kan ge upphov till muskel- och skelettbiverkningar",
				"id": "x3_92",
				"text": "<table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong><div class=\"tableLine\">Typ av muskel- och </div><div class=\"tableLine\">skelettbiverkning</div></strong></p></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Läkemedel</strong></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>Smärtfri myopati</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Utan neuropati</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Glukokortikoider, <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">betablockerare</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Med neuropati</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Klorokin</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p>Smärtsam myopati</p></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Utan neuropati</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Statiner, fibrater, hiv-läke-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">medel, fluorokinoloner, <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">ciklosporin</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Med neuropati</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Vinkristin, amiodaron</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Rabdomyolys</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Statiner, fibrater,<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">hiv-läkemedel</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Osteonekros, <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">atypiska frakturer</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1071140\" data-text=\"bisfosfonater:frakturer;fraktur:bisfosfonater\"></a>Bisfosfonater, denosumab</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Perifera frakturer</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Glitazoner</div></td></tr></tbody></table>"
